==French==
===Noun===
'''Anglais''' (feminine: [[Anglaise]], plural: Anglais, feminine plural: [[Anglaises]])

#male [[English]] person
#:''Cet '''Anglais''' ne parle pas français.'' - This English man does not speak French.
#group of [[English]] people (as soon as there is one male among them)
#:''Ces '''Anglais''' ne parlent pas français.'' - These English people do not speak French.

